overview:
The Quo Vadis diary guarantee

In choosing a Quo Vadis diary, you choose quality workmanship. We guarantee that you will be completely satisfied with your purchase because we offer:

  • A superior quality paper, smooth, extra white, no acid and writing does not go through.

  • A large choice of grids to suit you: If you would like a diary with a day to a page or if you prefer one week on 2 pages vertical or horizontal with/or without spaces for notes, we have what your need in an August to July or a January to December version.

  • Spaces for notes, category for telephone numbers, faxes, and email addresses to name a few. Everything has been thought of, so your diary follows you in all your daily activities.

  • All the important dates (Stats holiday, commemoration days etc) during the year are referenced.

  • A variety of covers changing from year to year for our customer’s satisfaction.
